age-text\">&lt;img src=&quot;image_src&quot; height=&quot;100px&quot; width=&quot;300px&quot;&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"이미지-정렬하기\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80-%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"이미지 정렬하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이미지 정렬하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"가운데-정렬하기\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%80%EC%9A%B4%EB%8D%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"가운데 정렬하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>가운데 정렬하기</h3>\n<p>마찬가지로 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img&gt;</code> 태그로 이미지를 첨부하고, 이미지 태그를 p태그로 감싼다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;image_src&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"오른쪽-정렬하기-왼쪽-정렬하기\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%A4%EB%A5%B8%EC%AA%BD-%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-%EC%99%BC%EC%AA%BD-%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"오른쪽 정렬하기 왼쪽 정렬하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" foc